props.name: summary
props.description: Text to use within the summary element (the visible part of the details element). If content is provided in the `summary` slot, this prop will be ignored.

props.name: text
props.description: Text to use within the disclosed part of the details element. If content is provided in the default slot, this prop will be ignored.

props.name: id
props.description: ID to add to the details element.

props.name: modelValue
props.description: The open state of the details element. In most cases you should use `v-model` instead of setting this prop directly.

slots.name: summary
slots.description: The content of the summary element (the visible part of the details element). If content is provided in this slot, the `summary` prop will be ignored.

slots.name: default
slots.description: The content of the disclosed part of the details element. If content is provided in this slot, the `text` prop will be ignored.
